{
  "stem": "26576.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "About for me, it was a great achievement, and it helped me a lot later on in life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but the Russian Jews, as we know it now, were better assimilated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were-- they had a big sympathy for us, and there was a sense of Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a very good-- there were no synagogues.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't think that I remember anybody at that stage going to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't even remember seeing a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- but as I said, Merke wasn't an old beautiful city like later on when we went to Dzambul, Merke was a city, but a new on and so-- and was-- I'll tell you another story.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't remember even having toilets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember the doors half built or houses in the wintertime we used to go into this house and we urinated there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The sanitation was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is why there were so many sicknesses around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were no synagogues.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think that people would be scared to go to a synagogue, even if there would be one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember in school those were the times of Stalin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were-- so it was everything was around Stalin, and Stalin was our hero.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I even wanted to join, at a certain stage, I wanted to join the Pioneers, which was the youth of the Communist party.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my father said absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because if I would join, that might not be-- so-- that might keep up back in Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was dreaming that the time will come that we'll go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wanted to join, because one likes to belong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One wants to be a part.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody in school was a Pioneer or a Komsomol.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
